// Man page for pwgen
manPwgen="PWGEN(1)                         X Shell Manual                         PWGEN(1)

<b>NAME</b>
    pwgen - is used to generate passwords
<b>SYNOPSIS</b>
    <b>pwgen</b>
    Generate a password (15 chars).
    <b>pwgen </b><b>-s</b>
    Generate a hard password (20 chars).
    <b>pwgen </b><b>-l </b><b>NUMBER</b>
    Generate a password with NUMBER chars."